          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "過場動畫與預告",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 1,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "3.3版本預告：「六入盡明，諸相皆無」",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/02/10/142453215/308a556a3922c31a6eb39f4939d991a3_8623706935925513938.png"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "2022年11月25日",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "稻妻自古以來就不少怪談傳說。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "有些自然與世代傳承的鬼怪大妖脫不了關係；",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "而有些，也許只是舊時遺事的蒼涼一角…",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "YouTube：",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "劇情預告-「秋津羽戲」",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/05/142453215/e418ce0df87e907a51be41dc89c21568_5686981907590565404.png"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "2022年12月19日",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "簡單來說，以羽子板擊球打靶，考驗速度、耐性與方向控制力，即為「秋津羽戲」。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "此番遊藝可以單人玩耍，但若想合作或比試，可要找個有默契的同伴才能盡興。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "YouTube：",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "5.4版本預告：「夢間見月明」",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/02/07/142453215/9b343d2594fb3fba2a4551796b6e6991_1865611233134467642.png"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "2025年1月24日",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "人生就像穿梭在美夢與噩夢之間。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "感覺到緊張、恐懼、無法喘息的時刻，",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "請稍作休息，品嚐美夢的甘甜，",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "並將噩夢揉碎咀嚼。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Youtube：",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    }
